      "name": "FDA pump hemolysis correlation — 5 operating points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index compared against FDA benchmark experimental data at 5 flow-speed combinations. Mean absolute error 8.3%; all predictions within ±15% band. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at worst-case operating point (4 L/min, 3500 rpm)."
