      "name": "Mesh independence study — hemolysis scalar transport",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study (2.1M, 5.8M, 14.2M cells) demonstrates asymptotic convergence of the hemolysis index. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI < 3.2% on the QoI. Discretization error contribution judged acceptable for MRL 2."
    },
