      "description": "Sensitivity analysis comparing SST k-omega and realizable k-epsilon turbulence closures across the 5 operating points. Maximum hemolysis index deviation 6.1%. SST k-omega selected as primary model based on superior near-wall resolution of high-shear impeller passages."
    }
