      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature benchmarks for rotating blood-contacting devices. Hemolysis model form sensitivity assessed by comparing Giersiepen-Wurzinger and Zhang power-law coefficients; maximum QoI sensitivity 9.4%. Model form uncertainty judged acceptable for MRL 2."
